Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.36,1:38:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's almost a psychopath.\NLast time I think it was a woman. People
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.56,1:38:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,think, "Oh, women, women don't do that."\NYeah, they're women psychopaths, too.
