Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.84,1:38:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're ahead.\NQuit when you're ahead. People push the
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.67,1:38:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,greed button to the point 100,000 a year\Nisn't enough. Got to push push push push
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.52,1:38:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,push to 105, push to 110. Of course,\Nthen they get fired.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.44,1:38:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit when you're ahead.\NLet go of greed. That's the hard one.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.28,1:38:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And greed is that rapacious\Nwantingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.67,1:38:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Invoke your Buddha nature\Nand cleverly live in the space beneath
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.60,1:38:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,thoughts. People say, "How can I get the\Nmind to stop?" You don't have to get the
