Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.19,1:39:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll notice that thoughts are like the\Nsurface of the sea. And beneath the
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.96,1:39:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,surface of the sea is the stillness of\Nthe deep.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.84,1:39:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Beneath thoughts there is absolute\Nsilence.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.52,1:39:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now this voice is talking.\NWith spiritual advancement you become
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.11,1:39:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,aware that everything is happening\Nautonomous autonomously of its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.71,1:39:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to talk. The talkingness is\Nhappening isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.63,1:39:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that talkingness is happening of its\Nown.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.08,1:39:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need a me that's talking. I just\Nwitness that talkingness is happening of
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.23,1:39:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,its own.\NSo most of the things we worry about and
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.92,1:39:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,take blame for and feel guilty over are\Nfrankly autonomous. Autonomous. They
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.15,1:39:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,happen of their own nature.\NJust like a seed opens up and sprouts of
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.67,1:40:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,its own nature when it's time for it to\Ndo so. So there's no point of hovering
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.00,1:40:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,over it, trying to hurry it up or trying\Nto slow it down in its own due time
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.08,1:40:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,which is karmically deter determined\Nincluding when you leave the universe
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.36,1:40:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,leave this world.\NWhen you leave this world, we've done
