Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.44,1:41:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,at the beginning of time. resist.\NTherefore, it's because each one of us
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.92,1:41:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is part of God's creation\Nfrom the beginning of all time, the
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.88,1:42:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,beginning of creation.\NThere's not a then and a now.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.56,1:42:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In the infinite world of consciousness,\Nall places are here. All time is now.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.11,1:42:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing like then.\NAnd now everything is now.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.28,1:42:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In an infinite field of consciousness,\Nthere's no here or there. Every place is
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.48,1:42:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,equally the center. Every place is\Nequally here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.44,1:42:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Any point in time is now.\NAs you can see, when you're dealing with
