Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.15,1:42:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,out the window. All time is now.\NAll time is now.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.44,1:42:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get crazy, and everybody gets\Ncrazy. Anybody here thinks they don't
