Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.60,1:43:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I look at myself in the mirror. I can\Nvaguely see myself anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.04,1:43:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I see some older. I said, "God, you're\Nlooking like you're starting to look
