Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.08,1:44:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I still had the image from when I was in\N30s or something. Big mop of hair, you
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.08,1:44:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,know, everybody had moppy hair in those\Ndays.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.60,1:44:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak saintly to yourself in the mirror.\NGive yourself a lecture and and be kind
